---
import site from '../../site.config.json';
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---
<Page title={`About ${site.BRAND}`} description={`Who builds and maintains ${site.BRAND}.`}>
  <p>{site.BRAND} is an independent publication owned and operated by {site.legalEntity}.</p>
  <h2>What this site is</h2>
  <p>We build practical, free tools and plain-spoken guides for this topic. Everything here exists to answer real questions with specific, checkable information — not to pad out search results.</p>
  <h2>Who builds it</h2>
  <p>{site.BRAND} is built and maintained by the Trilot team — Rami Steitieh, building online since 1997, with editorial and engineering support. We research the topics we cover, build and test the tools ourselves, and cite sources we have actually checked.</p>
  <h2>How we make money</h2>
  <p>The tools and guides are free. We sell a paid digital guide, and some pages may carry advertising or clearly disclosed affiliate links. None of that changes what we recommend.</p>
  <p>Questions? See our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a> or read our <a href="/editorial/">editorial policy</a>.</p>
</Page>
